SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend House Bill No. 4248 on Page 1, Lines 16 through 17, by deleting all language and
inserting the following language, and amending the title to conform:
“ No person shall knowingly sell, deliver, or furnish any beverage containing hemp to any
person under twenty-one (21) years of age, or possess any beverage containing hemp if under
twenty-one (21) years of age.”
